A laymans explanation for n00bs (like myself)
extract this file into your $HOME directory
read the README to then follow these 3 commands in your terminal after extracting the 8485.sh into HOME:

mkdir -p ~/.local/bin
mv 8485  ~/.local/bin/8485
chmod +x ~/.local/bin/8485

You will now be able to run 8485 in any DIR through the terminal. ty for being interested in my first project!
